title: Iko Iko (Side by Side - RSD) Grateful Dead Dr John Dixie Cups
description:
Side By Side: Records Store Day single

Grateful Dead / Dr John / The Dixie Cups
Initial release : 2013


Side A:

    Iko Iko - Grateful Dead 

Side B:

    Iko Iko - Dr. John
    Iko Iko - The Dixie Cups 


A 7", colored vinyl, single comprising three versions of Iko Iko. This single was released as part of record store day on April 20, 2013. The source of the Grateful Dead version of Iko Iko is not known.
